\s EWE NCUTI YANJE URI NGAHA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ewe ncuti yanje uri ngaha wiyemeje gukurikira, Umwami Yesu aho uzoba hose, mu muriro canke mu rupfu, shir’umutima kw’isezerano.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uwusezerana ntashitse ameze nk’umuguruka, utwarwa n’umuyaga;\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit none ko wasezeraniye Uhoraho, k’uzomushingir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit intahe hose \bdit*\bdit k’uzogendana nawe hose shir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umutima kw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit sezerano\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Washinze intahe umunsi wabatizwa, imbere y’Imana n’imbere y’abantu, kugiye kwemangir’Umwami Yesu, Mu mibabaro canke mu marushwa shir’umutima kw’isezerano.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uwusezerana ntashitse ameze nk’umuguruka, utwarwa n’umuyaga;\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit none ko wasezeraniye Uhoraho, k’uzomushingir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit intahe hose k’uzogendana nawe hose shir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umutima kw’\bdit*\bdit I\bdit*\bdit sezerano\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Ntuz’igihe uzomara kw’isi ntuz’umunsi Yesu azozira, ntuz’umunsi wawe wo kwimurwa, none bite niwadendebukirwa? \bd*\bd Shir’umutima kw’isezerano.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uwusezerana ntashitse ameze nk’umuguruka, utwarwa n’umuyaga;\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit none ko wasezeraniye Uhoraho, k’uzomushingir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit intahe hose k’uzogendana nawe hose shir’umutima kw’Isezerano\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Iyambure ubunebwe mu rugendo, ugir’umwete mu vya Mpwemu, Iyambure umugenzo mu vy’Ijambo, wuzure uguhishurirwa, ubone gushika amahoro.\bd*
\pc \bdit Uwusezerana ntashitse ameze nk’umuguruka, utwarwa n’umuyaga;\bdit*\bd  \bd*\bdit none ko wasezeraniye Uhoraho, k’uzomushingir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit intahe hose k’uzogendana nawe hose shir’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit umutima kw’Isezerano\bdit*\bd .\bd*
\zoli1 \bd Ntuhengamire iburyo canke I bumoso, ntuhengamire mu vy’umubiri, ntuhengamire mu vya Mpwemu, n’ukorere agakiza kawe, uhind’agashitsi imbere y’Uhoraho.\bd*
